title: Dexter (TV Series) Season 1 Soundtrack - FLAC
description:
Season 1 Soundtrack from the 2006 TV Series Dexter in flac format.
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0773262/

Sadly the muppet who mastered the soundtrack compressed the fuck out most tracks so a lot of the dynamics are lost in the acoustic tracks, but meh... Ripped to flac and uploaded here since only mp3 versions were available and they had been compressed (volume-wise, not filesize) further, causing clipping and distortion in some tracks.


Will be seeding for a while until there's enough secondary seeds. Upstream is 50K/sec so speeds will be so-so right off the bat. Don't bitch, it will be continuously seeded for a while. Whining for more seeds won't make it go faster so kindly stfu.


EDIT: Whoopsie. Forgot the tagging. For those in need of them, gracenote's auto-tagger (included by default in winamp if you're unsure) has no problems grabbing the correct tags.
